               </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="welcome-text">
            <h1>"Unleash Your <span>Entertainment</span> Odyssey!"</h1>
            <a href="/event">Explore</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <h1>Welcome to the home page</h1>
</body>
</html>
